"append:choice[5]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as "
"Admiral Tully in the center. \"The RECLAIM and SALVAGE ASSOCIATION... or was"
" it RECYCLING? Anyway, I know about the dealings between the Federation and "
"your association, and while I personally do not approve of morally grey "
"companies, it'd seem we have one big transaction to take care of - get rid "
"of the Flagship and I'll make sure there will be compensation.\""

